# Vehicle API Tests

### Test Authentication (Get Token First)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@example.com",
    "password": "password"
}

### Get All Vehicles
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/vehicles
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### Create New Vehicle with Company Name
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/vehicles
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "plate_number": "TEST-456",
    "vehicle_type": "Van",
    "vehicle_owner": "Test Owner",
    "vehicle_owner_address": "123 Test Street, Test City",
    "vehicle_brand": "Toyota",
    "company_name": "DITO TELECOMMUNITY CORPORATION",
    "vehicle_status": "active",
    "add_date_in_company": "2025-08-29",
    "creation_date": "2025-08-29"
}

### Get Specific Vehicle
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/vehicles/TEST-456
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### Update Vehicle with Company Name
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/vehicles/TEST-456
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "plate_number": "TEST-456",
    "vehicle_type": "Van",
    "vehicle_owner": "Test Owner Updated",
    "vehicle_owner_address": "456 Updated Street, Updated City",
    "vehicle_brand": "Toyota",
    "company_name": "CHINA COMMUNICATION SERVICES PHILIPPINES CORPORATION",
    "vehicle_status": "active",
    "add_date_in_company": "2025-08-29",
    "creation_date": "2025-08-29"
}

### Delete Vehicle
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/vehicles/TEST-456
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
